title: AB 1200 Demo
description:
Have you thought of keeping cold drinks nearby to enjoy whenever you want?
The AB-1200 Beverage Cooler from Newair is the solution.

This beverage refrigerator has received a lot of good reviews, people really like how well it works, and how convenient it is to keep their drinks right nearby. It can hold up to 126 cans, and the 5 removable racks can be repositioned to accommodate larger things like bottles, or if you want to chill your craft brews to perfection. It makes a great beer cooler.

This beverage center is really quiet, one reviewer said you don’t even know it’s on. It’s free-standing, so it can go almost anywhere; you can set it up in the game room, or your bar if you want. 

There are 7 individual thermostat settings, so you can really keep your drinks at the temperature you like. This Beer cooler ranges from 34 to 64 degrees; making it possible to get your beverages pretty cold. It’s built to last, made of sturdy metal. It has thick insulation, a double-pane glass door that’s reversible, so you can set it up to open either way.

And it has LED lighting that doesn’t effect the temperature; we’ve received reviews that it looks really great at night. This beverage refrigerator makes a great showcase for your collection.

The video will tell you more about the AB-1200 Beverage Cooler from Newair.
